va]]''\n|Producer<br/>Distributor\n|-\n|2007||''[[Panthaya Kozhi]]''\n|Producer<br/>Distributor\n|-\n|2007||''[[Nivedyam (2007 film)|Nivedyam]]''\n|Distributor\n|-\n|2007||''[[Kangaroo (2007 film)|Kangaroo]]''\n|Distributor\n|-\n|2008||''[[Cycle (2008 film)|Cycle]]''\n|Distributor\n|-\n|2008||''[[Thalappavu]]''\n|Distributor\n|-\n|2009||''[[2 Harihar Nagar]]''\n|Producer<br/>Distributor\n|-\n|2010||''[[In Ghost House Inn]]''\n|Producer<br/>Distributor\n|-\n|2010||''[[Elsamma Enna Aankutty]]''\n|Distributor\n|-\n|2010||''[[Tournament \u2013 Play & Replay]]''\n|Producer\n|-\n|2011||''[[Salt N' Pepper]]''\n|Distributor\n|-\n|2011||''[[Violin (2011 film)|Violin]]''\n|Distributor\n|-\n|2017||''[[Honey Bee 2: Celebrations]]''\n|Producer\n|}\n\n===Other crew credits===\n*1987: ''[[Manivathoorile Aayiram Sivarathrikal]]'' \u2013 Script supervisor and [[assistant director]] (as [[Siddique\u2013Lal]])\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n<ref name=\"Mathrubhumi_1\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.mathrubhumi.com/english/story.php|archiveurl=http://archive.today/20130628014552/http://www.mathrubhumi.com/english/story.php?id=19303|archive-date=28 June 2013|url-status=dead|title=Mathrubhumi English - Acting is easy, direction most satisfying: Filmmaker Lal}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb name|0482309}}\n* [http://saltnpeppermedia.com/salt/lal.html Lal Actor/ Director SNP Database]\n\n{{National Film Award Special Mention feature film}}\n{{Kerala State Film Award for Best Actor}}\n{{FilmfareMalayalamBestActor}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lal}}\n[[Category:Malayalam film directors]]\n[[Category:Male actors from Kochi]]\n[[Category:1958 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Kerala State Film Award winners]]\n[[Category:Malayalam screenwriters]]\n[[Category:Male actors in Malayalam cinema]]\n[[Category:Indian male film actors]]\n[[Category:Filmfare Awards South winners]]\n[[Category:Indian male screenwriters]]\n[[Category:Film directors from Kochi]]\n[[C